<item>
            <title>[LU-3258] Command Line Tools</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3258</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;the following command line tools will be provided:&lt;br/&gt;
1. lfs raid1_merge&lt;br/&gt;
2. lfs raid1_split&lt;br/&gt;
3. lfs raid1_resync&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Creating replication files directly won&apos;t be supported in this phase, because write to replication is not supported, it will be impossible to get a non-zero sized replication file.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
